AMIA CO LTD (8438)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 40.75% to NT$120,935,000 from NT$204,110,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            120,935          204,110    
YOY%             -40.75%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            593,202          762,431    
YOY%             -22.20% 
=================================================================
 